RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO, COUNTERPARTY, CUSTOMER_NAME1, CURRENCY, PRODUCT_CODE, MODULE, BRANCH, SSI_MNEMONIC, PAY_AC_BRANCH, PAY_ACCOUNT, PAY_ACCOUNT_CCY, RECV_AC_BRANCH, RECV_ACCOUNT, RECV_ACCOUNT_CCY, ACC_WITH_INSTN1, BENEF_INSTITUTION1, ULT_BENEFICIARY1 FROM OLTM_INSTR A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY AND COUNTERPARTY = ? AND A.CURRENCY = ? AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' and A.record_stat = 'O' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO or RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)

SELECT distinct c.ccy_code, c.ccy_name FROM cytms_ccy_defn c, lbtbs_borrower_ccy l WHERE c.ccy_code = l.ccy AND l.contract_ref_no = ? AND l.ccy not in (SELECT currency FROM TLTB_EXT_CPTY_CURR_DET a WHERE a.COUNTERPARTY = ? AND a.cusip = ?)

select b.entity entity_id, b.entity_name, b.entity_type, b.PHONE_NO, b.FAX_NO, b.EMAIL from oltms_customer_entity a, oltms_customer_entity_details b where a.customer_no = ? and a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and b.customer_no = a.customer_no and b.entity not in (select entity_id from TLTB_EXT_CPTY_ENTITY c where c.COUNTERPARTY = ? AND c.cusip = ?)
